		<autolevel level="18">
			<feature optional="YES">
				<name>Draconic Bloodline: Draconic Presence</name>
				<text>Beginning at 18-го level, you can channel the dread presence of your dragon ancestor, causing those around you to become awestruck или frightened. As an action, you can spend 5 sorcery points to draw on this power и exude an aura of awe или fear (your choice) to a distance of 60 feet. For 1 minute или until you lose your concentration (as if you were casting a concentration spell), each hostile creature that starts its turn in this aura must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw или be charmed (if you chose awe) или frightened (if you chose fear) until the aura ends. A creature that succeeds on this saving throw is immune to your aura for 24 hours.</text>
			</feature>
			<feature optional="YES">
				<name>Wild Magic: Spell Bombardment</name>
				<text>Beginning at 18-го level, the harmful energy of your spells intensifies. When you roll damage for a spell и roll the highest number possible on any of the dice, choose one of those dice, roll it again и add that roll to the damage. You can use the feature only once per turn.</text>
			</feature>
			<feature optional="YES">
				<name>Favored Soul: Power of the Chosen</name>
				<text>Starting at 18-го level, when you cast one of the spells you learned from your Chosen of the Gods class feature, you regain hit points equal to your модификатор Харизмы (minimum of +1) + the spell's level.</text>
			</feature>
