			</feature>
			<feature optional="YES">
				<name>Shadow: Shadow Form</name>
				<text>At 18-го level, you can spend 3 sorcery points to transform yourself into a shadow form as a bonus action. In this form, you have resistance to all damage except force damage, и you can move through other creatures и objects as if they were difficult terrain. You take 5 force damage if you end your turn inside an object. You remain in this form for 1 minute.</text>
			</feature>
